                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7667" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1201</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3671 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创新求变：A发电企业碳预算体系的创建之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Innovation and Change: The Road to Create a Carbon Budget System for Power Generation Enterprise A</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宋晓华，余中福，万凌寒，皇甫豫冬，黄思琪</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华北电力大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">开滦协鑫发电有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“双碳”目标；碳预算；发电企业；全面预算体系；2023百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“Carbon Peaking and Carbon neutrality” goals; carbon budget; power generation enterprises; master budget</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“双碳”战略背景下，发电企业亟需推进能源转型，通过提高火电机组发电效率、积极布局可再生能源等方式，完成碳减排任务，实现低碳化发展的目标。为了在实现碳减排目标的同时保持盈利，A发电企业根据《中国发电企业温室气体排放核算方法与报告指南（试行）》等政策，在充分掌握企业碳排放活动、碳减排活动和碳排放权交易活动的具体情况后，以传统全面预算体系架构为基础，创新性构建了与企业业务流程相匹配的碳预算体系，并将其作为一个新的模块嵌入至全面预算体系中。本案例具体阐述了碳预算构建的基本流程、碳预算子预算表的设计、碳预算体系与全面预算体系的关系等内容。拟带领学生了解发电企业所面临的宏观环境和行业环境，熟悉我国发电企业碳排放核算与碳排放权交易的相关规定，掌握碳预算编制的基本流程与方法，理解融入碳预算的全面预算体系的构成逻辑，为发电企业通过管理会计的相关理论与方法推进低碳绿色转型提供参考，也为其他行业进行碳预算管理、升级全面预算体系提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In order to achieve “Carbon Peaking and Carbon neutrality” goals, power generation companies urgently need to promote energy transformation. By improving the power generation efficiency of thermal power units and actively deploying renewable energy, they can complete the task of carbon emission reduction and achieve the goal of low-carbon development. In order to maintain profitability while achieving the carbon emission reduction target, power generation company A fully grasps the specific conditions of the company&#39;s carbon emission activities, carbon emission reduction activities and carbon emission trading activities, and builds a carbon budget system that matches the business process of the enterprise, and embedded it into the master budget system as a new module.
This case specifically describes the basic process of building the carbon budget system, the design of the carbon budget sub-budget table and the relationship between the carbon budget system and the master budget system. It is planned to lead students to understand the macro environment and industry environment faced by power generation enterprises, to be familiar with the relevant regulations on carbon emission accounting and carbon emission trading, to master the basic process and method of carbon budget preparation, to understand the logic of the composition of the master budget system integrated into the carbon budget. The case provides reference for power generation enterprises to promote carbon emission reduction and green transformation through the relevant theories and methods of management accounting, and also provides reference for carbon budget management conduction and the master budget system’s upgrade in other industries.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理会计》、《环境会计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">PEST分析基本原理；波特五力分析模型；碳预算概念及作用；碳排放量核算方法；碳减排量及成本核算方法；碳交易损益核算方法；全面预算管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
